                        <interp inst="t18480131-675-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 59.—<hi rend="italic">Recommended to mercy by the Prosecutor and Jury.—
